"IMPROVED INVISIBLITY"

Category: ^gILLUSION^n
Duration: ^gSUSTAINED^n

Improved Invisiblity prevents removes you from the visual spectrums
of all living and non-living things. Any sound you make can still be 
heard. 

It can be counteracted by ultrasound or viewing the astral plane.

^WSee Also: CAST, INVISIBIILITY^n
